definitions.definition: A city in southern Alberta , Canada , the fourth-largest in the province, from William Lethbridge, president of the North Western Coal and Navigation Company
A community near Clarenville , Newfoundland and Labrador .
A rural township in Golden Plains Shire, near Geelong , Victoria , Australia .
